{"tid":1963893,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支衛否認偏袒中共 稱不是削減資助的時候","createTime":"2020-04-08T12:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T13:07:43.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"20a56b51160871867c4dce935908694e2e66c36e","tid":1963893,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"世衛否認偏袒中國 稱不是削減資助的時候<br />\n08.04.2020 20:12<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普批評世衛組織，太以中國為中心，疫情期間多次作出錯誤評估，會審視是否暫緩向世衛提供資金。世衛總幹事譚德塞的高級顧問艾爾沃德否認偏袒中國，指新型冠狀病毒在武漢爆發初期，與中國合作很重要，以了解疫情，指世衛同其他疫情重災區，例如西班牙的合作，同中國的並無分別。世衛歐洲區主任克魯格指，現時處於疫情大流行的危急階段，並非削減世衛資金的時候。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279610&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279610%26csid%3D261_367&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBa0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=4dfb5d86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279610&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"cda8e777ae4d0881f6cabc375bf520a695e9ad0c","tid":1963893,"uid":124410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:24:09.000Z","msg":"知驚？"},{"pid":"f2b0c1588dd5db64b5212390c6af35d69a3fad86","tid":1963893,"uid":221171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"鳳x衛視記者係外國勢力面前帶頭搞港獨 違反一中原則 記者唔該問下局長點睇"},{"pid":"3632c34477c279d0171f2313101c37efcc373bb6","tid":1963893,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />承認先報新聞啦"},{"pid":"a2543dee21ebd0d442a5355a9b8f4e22ffb6b294","tid":1963893,"uid":5737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得係時候收你皮先真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998cc4856c86cd43005957329cfe7337aa3f